{"id": "1220242952195014656", "channel_id": "1219878243369353287", "type": 19, "author_id": "232848201500065792", "author_name": "hananichiya", "author_bot": false, "content": "阿紅打庫姆\n阿紅\n打 庫 姆\n好像我落地打兩隻小怪能營運出黃金造物一樣", "timestamp": "2024-03-21T05:29:50.821000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-03-21T05:30:26.949000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [{"emoji": "✅", "emoji_id": null, "count": 1}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1220242792958136340", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1219878243369353287", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅茶會：關於遊戲樂趣平衡性理念", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1220243171276230777", "channel_id": "1219878243369353287", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "各種角度上確實沒毛病……哈哈哈。以前我還有人說感受到了魂系遊戲的味。這方面可能沒辦法，希望能在其他地方盡可能彌補各位的感受。", "timestamp": "2024-03-21T05:30:43.054000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["456226577798135808"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1219971497595244695", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1219878243369353287", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅茶會：關於遊戲樂趣平衡性理念", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1220243679696916500", "channel_id": "1219878243369353287", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "劣勢對局仍然會在，不過我們會關注一下這個程度是否合理，謝謝！", "timestamp": "2024-03-21T05:32:44.271000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["232848201500065792"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1220242952195014656", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1219878243369353287", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅茶會：關於遊戲樂趣平衡性理念", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1220244765027733594", "channel_id": "1219878243369353287", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "上面聊過了這個問題。我們會研究一下。單個隊伍是更可能遇到阻力，尤其是在非主線環境。主線中我們確保了初始陣容的可能性，並且養成材料較低，非常推薦大家培養作為備選。", "timestamp": "2024-03-21T05:37:03.034000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1213843511707705425"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1219972753734766612", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1219878243369353287", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅茶會：關於遊戲樂趣平衡性理念", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1220245108373590057", "channel_id": "1219878243369353287", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "這是合理比例的問題。有傾向當然是正常的。極端唯一選擇則不利。我們從未以單一維度衡量。這也正是這個遊戲平衡性難處理的特點之一。", "timestamp": "2024-03-21T05:38:24.894000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1034259288874549298"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1219974337256489020", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1219878243369353287", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅茶會：關於遊戲樂趣平衡性理念", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1220245288015364106", "channel_id": "1219878243369353287", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "謝謝你的意見。我們也是如此考慮的。雖然仍然無法保證一定不會出現削弱，但我們今後對造物也會更謹慎，更多的溝通。", "timestamp": "2024-03-21T05:39:07.724000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["428434526327406602"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1219979182814269553", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1219878243369353287", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅茶會：關於遊戲樂趣平衡性理念", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1220245445985697802", "channel_id": "1219878243369353287", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "謝謝你覺得我們的遊戲有趣，會繼續努力的！", "timestamp": "2024-03-21T05:39:45.387000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["456226577798135808"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1219980916655525948", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1219878243369353287", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅茶會：關於遊戲樂趣平衡性理念", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1220245903223296100", "channel_id": "1219878243369353287", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "會考慮的！謝謝你。順便，那不是什麼羈絆，是同調率！同調率！！！", "timestamp": "2024-03-21T05:41:34.401000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1051752197244866681"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1220019148059443210", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1219878243369353287", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅茶會：關於遊戲樂趣平衡性理念", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1220246593534427206", "channel_id": "1219878243369353287", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "評論可能要更晚，目前沒有具體的時間。流血的應對方法就是治療，因此暫時沒有繼續出流血對策的計劃。 流血機制本身我們有在一些地方嘗試作為我方機制，希望未來有機會進一步挖掘！", "timestamp": "2024-03-21T05:44:18.984000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["960539649498042408"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1220027616006901880", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1219878243369353287", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅茶會：關於遊戲樂趣平衡性理念", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1220247192539889736", "channel_id": "1219878243369353287", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "確實如此，所以我們最初也給很多東西沒有做限制。但是這樣爆炸組合效應，可能就會有一個顯著優勢很大的玩法出現，碾壓其他一切正常玩法的成果，最後會覺得我用心研究的玩法不值一提，這樣也會讓人帶來更大的失望和更單一的體驗。這個度可能在各個問題上尺度不同。通常擁有上限則要大幅減少這樣的可能性。", "timestamp": "2024-03-21T05:46:41.798000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["386730481502257153"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1220028712507146342", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1219878243369353287", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅茶會：關於遊戲樂趣平衡性理念", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1220247561617539072", "channel_id": "1219878243369353287", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "我們在努力避免這一點。對於我們遊戲，如果數值持續膨脹，出牌，計算力量等的負擔就會越來越大。", "timestamp": "2024-03-21T05:48:09.793000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["546511962977337344"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1220067835292811366", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1219878243369353287", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅茶會：關於遊戲樂趣平衡性理念", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
