{"id": "1220248157217099797", "channel_id": "1219878243369353287", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "謝謝你的分享。會參考的。", "timestamp": "2024-03-21T05:50:31.795000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["757961390412660836"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1220221133710819338", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1219878243369353287", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅茶會：關於遊戲樂趣平衡性理念", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
{"id": "1220248846924513350", "channel_id": "1219878243369353287", "type": 19, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "造物本身之間的聯動性我們一直有考慮。這裡的問題就在於我們是誰的問題。我們是卡牌養成，也有肉鴿元素。因此角色與造物之間玩法構成上需要更加恰當。", "timestamp": "2024-03-21T05:53:16.234000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["1206302250356449290"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1219887969763201055", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1219878243369353287", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅茶會：關於遊戲樂趣平衡性理念", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
