{"id": "1220318908209430578", "channel_id": "1219878243369353287", "type": 0, "author_id": "660503452925034507", "author_name": "mate0321", "author_bot": false, "content": "会有新的界限突破的角色吗？界拉蒙娜还挺好玩的。希望能多出一些。", "timestamp": "2024-03-21T10:31:40.146000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1219878243369353287", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "✅茶會：關於遊戲樂趣平衡性理念", "forum_channel_id": "1184003940082262069"}
